c: 3
v: 151
t: "Tuzoshira ubwoba mumitima yabarya bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri, kubera ubugereranyi bwabo bw’Imana y’ukuri, hamwe n’abata manuriwe ivyemezo vyemeza iyo Mana, n’ubwicaro bwabo buzoba ari ubwo mu muriro udahera, nabwo n’ubwicaro bubi bumeze gute! kandi n’ubwicaro bw’abahemukiye imitima yabo"